  "detailed_description": "SLICE is a 2D game where you slice objects to solve puzzles. Slice through various unique levels full of mind-clicking experience. Use fun to explore gameplay mechanics to combine thinking with slicing.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840310/extras/bd45090a05d5ff48b31fbc06bd1f4a37.avif?t=1635454552\" width=604 height=158 /></span> <br><br><strong>Key Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Minimalistic visual design<br></li><li>Challenging and rewarding puzzles<br></li><li>Light and Dark versions of levels<br></li><li>Fun to discover gameplay mechanics<br></li><li>Original, atmospheric music<br></li><li>Meditative atmosphere<br></li><li> 2 FREE additional contents<br></li><li> 225 UNIQUE LEVELS  in total</li></ul><br><i>       Note: you should not do this if you want to solve the puzzle:</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840310/extras/935d3f2dc15f64aac4b150636aa85bd9.poster.avif?t=1635454552\" width=480 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840310/extras/935d3f2dc15f64aac4b150636aa85bd9.webm?t=1635454552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/840310/extras/935d3f2dc15f64aac4b150636aa85bd9.mp4?t=1635454552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
